OL,3,CFurther arrests made as investigation
OL,4,Cinto death of man outside bar continues
OL,6,FDorset Police have made further
OL,7,Farrests as officers continue to
OL,8,Finvestigate the death of a man outside
OL,9,Fa bar in Bournemouth.
OL,11,FPolice said they received a report of
OL,12,Fan assault outside MyBar in
OL,13,FCharminster Road at around 3am on
OL,14,FMonday 6 April.
OL,16,FA man, in his 40s, from Christchurch
OL,17,Fwas pronounced dead at the scene. His
OL,18,Fnext of kin has been told.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/6
