OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1775581553
OL,3,CFurther arrests made as investigation
OL,4,Cinto death of man outside bar continues
OL,6,FTwo men from Bournemouth, aged 37 and
OL,7,F46, and a 34-year-old man from Poole
OL,8,Fwere arrested on suspicion of murder.
OL,9,FPolice said they have all been
OL,10,Freleased under investigation.
OL,12,FAfter further enquiries, a fourth man,
OL,13,Faged 35 and from Bournemouth, was
OL,14,Flocated in the Bristol area and has
OL,15,Falso been arrested on suspicion of
OL,16,Fmurder. He is currently in police
OL,17,Fcustody.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/6
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,413,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1775581553
OL,3,CFurther arrests made as investigation
OL,4,Cinto death of man outside bar continues
OL,6,FA 39-year-old man from Bournemouth was
OL,7,Falso arrested on suspicion of
OL,8,Fassisting an offender and also remains
OL,9,Fin police custody.
OL,11,FDetective Chief Inspector Nicky
OL,12,FJenkins, of Dorset Police's Major
OL,13,FCrime Investigation Team, said: "We
OL,14,Fare continuing to carry out extensive
OL,15,Fenquiries into the circumstances of
OL,16,Fthis incident and our thoughts remain
OL,17,Fwith the family of the man who sadly
OL,18,Fdied.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/6
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
