OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,413,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1775581553
OL,3,CFurther arrests made as investigation
OL,4,Cinto death of man outside bar continues
OL,6,F"I am continuing to ask anyone who
OL,7,Fwitnessed any suspicious activity,
OL,8,Fcaptured any relevant footage or who
OL,9,Fhas any information that might assist
OL,10,Fus, to please get in touch.
OL,12,F"This fast-paced investigation has
OL,13,Fresulted in a number of arrests and
OL,14,Fcordons were put place as we gathered
OL,15,Fevidence. These cordons have now been
OL,16,Flifted and we continue to work to
OL,17,Festablish a full picture of what
OL,18,Fhappened.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/6
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
