PN,41205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1775581553
OL,3,CFurther arrests made as investigation
OL,4,Cinto death of man outside bar continues
OL,6,F"An increased police presence will
OL,7,Fremain in the area over the coming
OL,8,Fdays and we would encourage anyone
OL,9,Fwith information or concerns to please
OL,10,Fspeak with an officer."
OL,12,FAnyone with information is asked to
OL,13,Fcontact Dorset Police online or by
OL,14,Fcalling 101, quoting the number
OL,15,F55260048268.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/6
